devdoc.details: Simple smart contract to store and retrieve sales forecasting data Simplified structure: - Store historical and forecast data as simple arrays - Store metrics separately - Easy to integrate with frontend

getUserForecastTypes(address).details: Get all forecast types for a user

storeForecast(string,string[],uint256[],.details: Store forecast data (simplified - stores in batches to avoid stack issues)
